data.description:
HURRY SELLER WILL HELP WITH $5,000.00 TO CLOSSING COST Welcome to this well looking Home! This townhome has been fully renovated, with new carpet, new kitchen cabinets, laminated flooring and more!! It also has a new furnace and water heater and a nice private backyard. Do not miss the opportunity to come and explore all this property has to offer for your family! Great two-level unit, it has central air conditioning, an open floor plan with a lot of natural light.  Features include 3 bedrooms, a full bathroom,1 1/2 bathroom on main level. Washer/dryer, and all kitchen appliances are included. The attached 1-car garage has an extra storage closet. This community has a swimming pool and park area, playground and open area to enjoy the outdoors. Close to shops, restaurants and easy access to major highways. 
Please do not hesitate in contacting me for your private showing!
